# SpeedSight Champions

**SpeedSight Champions** is a fast-paced visual memory and reflex game designed to test your focus, attention, and reaction speed in real time.

A 4-digit number appears on the screen for a very brief moment. Your goal is to memorize it instantly and enter the correct code as fast as possible. The faster and more accurately you respond, the higher your score.

